    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的故事</strong></h2>作为种马场未来不情愿的继承人，开始你的冒险吧。证明你不仅仅是个被宠坏的孩子。从零开始，学习如何经营和管理种马场。这将是一项巨大的挑战，也将会有令人难以置信的回报，让种马场恢复往日的辉煌！在这场冒险之旅中，你会发现没有什么比与马建立的纽带更持久的了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/93eb6643bc333f7c5f4ed8b021b7429c.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/93eb6643bc333f7c5f4ed8b021b7429c.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/93eb6643bc333f7c5f4ed8b021b7429c.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理种马场，让其重现昔日辉煌！</strong></h2>你的种马场经营状况不佳，你的任务是重建马场，这要求相当多的养马场知识和技能。获取新知识并开发技能，使农场达到最佳状态，并学习如何经营马场。管理你的员工和马匹。让马场从废墟变成你和你马匹温暖的家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/71848598282941942b5dee3d0fcc413a.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/71848598282941942b5dee3d0fcc413a.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/71848598282941942b5dee3d0fcc413a.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的马不是你唯一可以交到的朋友！</strong></h2>骑上马，探索Chestnut Glen田园诗般的世界及其周边景观。四处走走并与村民们见面，与他们一起出去玩并完成他们的任务，以提高你和种马场的声誉，重建破败的种马场。请记住，并非你遇到的每个人都想与你成为朋友。有些人甚至不喜欢马！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/e97f9da15715d73024ff97651e596446.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/e97f9da15715d73024ff97651e596446.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/e97f9da15715d73024ff97651e596446.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的梦想之马</strong></h2>在My Horse: Bonded Spirits游戏中，你不仅可以改变你的外表，还可以改变你的马和种马场的外观。为你的马选择各种配饰、发型和马鞍，让你可以潇洒地驰骋世界。安置装饰品并翻新种马场，不仅可以美化马厩，还可以改造整个周边地区！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/6e8c41e0c1bb8c8c3dfa568666433cfe.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/6e8c41e0c1bb8c8c3dfa568666433cfe.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/6e8c41e0c1bb8c8c3dfa568666433cfe.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>参加各种比赛，证明实力</strong></h2>你认为与你马的良好关系足以让你赢得比赛吗？你们之间的信任度越高，你的马就越容易学习新技能，它对新挑战的恐惧就越少。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.poster.avif?t=1765377087\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.webm?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376970/extras/d6bd7b4ad5a6f989b0ab105205481d7f.mp4?t=1765377087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
